BOSONZ is a VOLTZ adjacent modpack based on HBM's NTM (nuclear tech mod).

The focus in on progressing trough technology while "protecting" yourself from your neighbors or destroying them for their wealth and territory.

[warn]I highly recommend playing this pack in PVP multiplayer it's designed this way. If you want a solo (and much better experience) go play GTNH or (insert generic create modpack here).[/warn]

I recommand exploring the different questlines quickly then heading to the main quests (TIER 1 to X).
